    "Alas, many cable locks are a pain to install, and the risk of being caught with your lock at the wrong angle prevents you from using it most of the time.",
    "There are also mechanical locks, with a U-shaped bar that locks behind the front wheel.",
    "This prevents cutting through the lock with bolt cutters, but the bar is hard to get in and out of place.",
    "Human: A few solid suggestions.",
    "It can be a sometimes to use two or more."
